AUDIENCE: One of
the cited downsides

00:39:18.100 --> 00:39:20.815
of doing manufacturing
in China, for example,

00:39:20.815 --> 00:39:23.985
is that there is a strong
black market of people

00:39:23.985 --> 00:39:26.542
who will copy the process
and [INAUDIBLE] factories

00:39:26.542 --> 00:39:27.504
after hours.

00:39:27.504 --> 00:39:29.820
If you start moving
manufacturing

00:39:29.820 --> 00:39:31.672
closer to the
consumers, is there

00:39:31.672 --> 00:39:35.050
a concern that companies will
only use older manufacturing

00:39:35.050 --> 00:39:35.550
processes?

00:39:35.550 --> 00:39:37.950
They won't do the
innovation where

00:39:37.950 --> 00:39:40.350
there are far more people
